'''''The Old Beauty and Others''''' is a collection of short stories by [[Willa Cather]], published in 1948.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kirjasto.sci.fi/wcather.htm |title=Wil(le)la (Siebert) Cather |website=Books and Writers ''(kirjasto.sci.fi)'' |first=Petri |last=Liukkonen |publisher=[[Kuusankoski]] Public Library |location=Finland |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110116075657/http://kirjasto.sci.fi/wcather.htm |archivedate=16 January 2011 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref>
==Contents== This collection contains the following stories:<ref>Worldcat.org, http://www.worldcat.org/title/old-beauty-and-others/oclc/000280656</ref> * The Old Beauty * The Best Years * Before Breakfast
